data.description: All your friends are going to be green with envy as they step into your stunningly remodeled masterpiece, where modern sophistication effortlessly intertwines with timeless charm.  Crafted by professional designer, the home emanates a sense of warmth, roominess, and serenity that you won’t find anywhere else.    Step into the open and inviting main space, anchored by a well equipped kitchen, that doesn’t feel crowded and includes all brand new cabinets, appliances, countertops, and hardware.  Watch over your little ones, catch the game, cook up a masterpiece, or simply sit at the bar and connect while everyone else does those things.  You can have it all.      The allure doesn’t end there - beautiful new flooring flows through three bedrooms and a bathroom, creating a cohesive and comforting atmosphere throughout.  As you venture outside past the laundry that includes a washer and brand new dryer, you’ll find yourself in a fully fenced and spacious yard that provides the ideal backdrop for gatherings, pets, or just your own tranquil escape.  With abundant off-street parking, a generously sized storage shed, and a brand new roof, your search for your next home ends here.    The final surprise is the butcher block countertops in the kitchen were left unfinished on purposes.  That’s so you can choose the final color and begin to transform the space into being all yours. There are samples of your options at the house and the seller will pay for and do that work before you move in.
